{"id": "1341803083419746324", "channel_id": "1341803083419746324", "type": 0, "author_id": "693745205777530880", "author_name": "lingcheng.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "反正這遊戲已經沒救了 每次覺得他都會道歉 當我們覺得他要改的時候 他又這麼幹了\n\n反正我先潤了", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T16:06:24.583000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 27}], "attachments": [{"id": "1341803083742842962", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-02-19-22-28-42-203_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 150520, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1341803083419746324/1341803083742842962/Screenshot_2025-02-19-22-28-42-203_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=6a00ad00&is=69ff5b80&hm=d551ca32bc4449aee0d0b72f9c9c79cfe2dd1e80e0d62a44dd048779ec3edca8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341803083419746324", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我覺得與其在這邊一直叫 不如直接一星期不上線+停止課金", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1341677655543775284", "channel_id": "1341677655543775284", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "之前红白卡的设计本身就是特色，而且描述更清晰，现在全部额外描述都没了，而且很容易搞混。", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T07:48:00.247000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341677655543775284", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "24能不能改回来啊，现在这个显示真的意义不明", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497", "1181168197425172480", "1181168183319736412"]}
{"id": "1341878552525672488", "channel_id": "1341878552525672488", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156964372397178960", "author_name": "taki002", "author_bot": false, "content": "卡牌策略遊戲就是要有多變、豐富的卡組，讓牌組構築帶來無限可能性，才能不斷地嘗試新的策略。你星辰篇大刀一砍什麼東西都死光，真正能上的了檯面的就那幾隊，這樣也叫做卡牌遊戲嗎?\n\n要不是你的美術頂尖，真以為玩家都喜歡在這裡受折磨。這美術同類型要找到能媲美的真的不多，但遊戲性設計的跟屎一樣，你們自己真的有玩過嗎?\n\n**現在的情況就是這遊戲有了資金，有了1-2年的更新計畫，所以限制玩家成長、限制膨脹數值就成了主要目的，最好舊的角色通通不能用，這樣才能逼玩家去抽新角色**\n\n勸你們趕緊想好遊戲要調整的方向，【星辰篇】這種東西多留一天都是餘毒，否則損失的玩家絕對會超過你們的想像\n\n\np.s.每場戰鬥都要消耗銀鑰才能覺醒卡牌的設計真的是爛透了", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T21:06:17.820000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-19T21:10:48.600000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1341879661738725451", "filename": "5aef1a5336e6b44f.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 152964, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1341878552525672488/1341879661738725451/5aef1a5336e6b44f.jpg?ex=6a004b92&is=69fefa12&hm=5b36c4ba04d10fd803ae4b8e6181dabe1b1b4f19895295c3d0e13005aee7a2f9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341878552525672488", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【星辰篇】這種東西多留一天都是餘毒", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497"]}
